      nit: 4
      jac: [ 4.470e-08]
 hess_inv: [[ 1.000e-02]]
     nfev: 14
     njev: 7
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
But, others don't.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="org-src-container"&gt;
&lt;pre class="src src-jupyter-python"&gt;get_minima(0.8)    
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

